# GitHub Linguist hints
#
# EmpiriForge is primarily a documentation and agent-skill workflow repository.
# These rules keep GitHub's language badge from over-weighting support scripts
# or rendered/prose artifacts as the repository's "main language".

*.md linguist-documentation
docs/** linguist-documentation
examples/** linguist-documentation
skills/**/SKILL.md linguist-documentation
skills/**/references/** linguist-documentation
skills/**/templates/** linguist-documentation
skills/**/scripts/*.ps1 linguist-documentation
